{"tid":1397217,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩佬：我在曼聯的成就被貶低","createTime":"2019-08-02T11:17:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T11:56:00.000Z","uid":16659,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4ee5ebe9ecc9bf4bf309954e48e1d440a0e54cb5","tid":1397217,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:17:30.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】去年被曼聯辭退的名帥摩連奴，似乎對在紅魔所獲的名聲心有不甘，認為沒得到應得的認同。<br />\n<br />\n「我可以說在曼聯的日子並不好過，我時常覺得贏歐霸盃是出類拔萃，但事實並不是這樣，人們可不是那樣想。」摩連奴受訪時顯得滿腹鬱悶，他於2016/17年率紅魔贏得歐霸盃，得以躋身緊接一季的歐聯。<br />\n<br />\n到了2017/18年球季，他帶領曼聯得到聯賽亞軍。「得到第2名就比那（歐霸盃冠軍）更為成功，所以我的感覺有點像『Wow，我工作得好，傾盡全力，而我沒有得到該得到的』。」<br />\n<br />\n早前已表明希望再戰球壇的他續說：「唯一我可以承諾的事，當我為下一個球會效力，下一份差事，我會相當，相當開心，帶著大笑容進入新聞發佈會。我可以作出承諾。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"157db57091516e95e170f698feeaefac251588b9","tid":1397217,"uid":16659,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:18:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/NQzgLgRFVm2i0DRS0C/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FNQzgLgRFVm2i0DRS0C%2Fgiphy.gif&h=856b49f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a425d75746c6062cf230209ce6170145033e461","tid":1397217,"uid":18646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:19:05.000Z","msg":"幾時有工開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7390993ec8030e7f387167305f02fdeed7b33888","tid":1397217,"uid":79562,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:21:14.000Z","msg":"不要不要假設我知道<br />\n一切一切也都是為我而做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDaddy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01ccf0863c9c9d695ba91a249b65c2a005e6a06","tid":1397217,"uid":40932,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"5a425d75746c6062cf230209ce6170145033e461","tid":1397217,"uid":18646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:19:05.000Z","msg":"